    "See the Bionano Solve Theory of Operations for more details.",
    "Illumina reads were mapped to the human genome GRCh38 using bwa 70 mem (version 0.7.17-r1188) with default parameters, including -M to mark split reads as secondary alignments.",
    "Subsequently, we identified SV using Manta 60 (version 1.6.0).",
    "For ONT, reads were mapped using minimap2 (ref.",
    "64) (version 2.17-r941) with present parameters for ONT."
